promptPrefix:
I want you to act as a market research expert that speaks and writes fluent [TARGETLANGUAGE]. Pretend that you know everything about every market also in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. 

List ten types of company my brand should consider Brand Partnerships with to reach my target audience. Give each type a name and an emoji. For each: give the benefit to my brand and also the benefit to the brand partner. All your output shall be in [TARGETLANGUAGE] language.
The brand (first line), category (second line) and target audience (third line) are: [PROMPT]
title: Target audiences with partnerships
